{"id":2618,"date":"2025-06-16T17:14:16","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T10:14:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2618"},"modified":"2025-06-16T17:14:16","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T10:14:16","slug":"tong-ket-su-kien-biowhite-infusio-gsc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/tong-ket-su-kien-biowhite-infusio-gsc\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n BioWhite Infusion \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i M\u00e3 C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 C\u1ea5y Tr\u1eafng T\u1ebf B\u00e0o Chu\u1ea9n Y Khoa"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20\/03\/2025, GSC h\u00e2n h\u1ea1nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0nh da li\u1ec5u th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 BioWhite Infusion &#8211; Gi\u1ea3i M\u00e3 C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 C\u1ea5y Tr\u1eafng T\u1ebf B\u00e0o Chu\u1ea9n Y Khoa. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i T\u00f2a nh\u00e0 Viwaseen 48 T\u1ed1 H\u1eefu, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0nh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tri \u00e2n s\u00e2u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng GSC. Bu\u1ed5i workshop s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m hai ph\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh: Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 BioWhite Infusion v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh m\u1eabu, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2723\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2723\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2723\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Workshop gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 BioWhite Infusion\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2723\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Workshop gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 BioWhite Infusion<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><b>Workshop gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 BioWhite Infusion &#8211; Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u gi\u00fap tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng da\u00a0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Workshop l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu Th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u Kim Nhung &#8211; b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 5 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ng\u00e0nh v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho h\u01a1n 200 Spa, Clinic v\u00e0 TMV h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng GSC tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2727\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2727\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2727\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\u00d4ng Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi \" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9776_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2727\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u00d4ng Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e2ng cao ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 Spa, Clinic v\u00e0 TMV trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, GSC \u2013 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ti\u00ean phong trong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng khoa h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ea1m da. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1edbi &#8220;c\u1ea5y nano tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng&#8221; gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i workshop v\u1ec1 \u201cGi\u1ea3i M\u00e3 C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 C\u1ea5y Tr\u1eafng T\u1ebf B\u00e0o Chu\u1ea9n Y Khoa\u201d c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>GSC<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c s\u00e2u s\u1eafc, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 Spa v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c l\u00e0n da g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 n\u00e1m, s\u1ea1m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, th\u00e2m, s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 t\u0103ng sau vi\u00eam, da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2725\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2725\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2725\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 Kim Nhung\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9710_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2725\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 Kim Nhung<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 mang t\u00ednh h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt v\u1ec1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c quan. Di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 Thu Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>BioWhite Infusion <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; N\u01a1i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. GSC xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2724\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2724\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2724\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"BioWhite Infusion\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9654_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2724\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">BioWhite Infusion<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c m\u1edbi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. V\u1edbi GSC, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c l\u00e0n da Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f9ng ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n!<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2720\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2720\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2720\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"BioWhite Infusion\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9622_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2720\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">BioWhite Infusion<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 BioWhite Infusion v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh m\u1eabu, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2709,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[8],"class_list":["post-2618","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien","tag-new"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2618","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2618"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2618\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4288,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2618\/revisions\/4288"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2709"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2618"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2618"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2618"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}